rows.label: tev066801_JNK0010
rows.name: Inquire

rows.label: tev066801_SEL0011
rows.name: Ask Zo Ozuchi what makes people strong.

rows.label: tev066801_JNK0020
rows.name: Discuss

rows.label: tev066801_SEL0021
rows.name: Ask Zo Ozuchi what he is doing.

rows.label: tev066801_SEL0031
rows.name: Ask Zo Ozuchi about Primordia.

rows.label: tev066801_SEL0041
rows.name: Ask Zo Ozuchi about recent developments.

rows.label: tev066801_MSG0001
rows.name:
I see many different strengths in people. The Wrothian
man who quests alone and proud... The Wrothian
woman who thirsts to avenge her brothers...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev066801_MSG0002
rows.name:
Then there is the one with the strange doppelganger
technique... Not to mention the Nopon woman with
confidence in her skills.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev066801_MSG0003
rows.name:
And forget not the Prone woman who betrayed her
Ganglion masters, or the green-skinned technician who
keeps our water safe. ...And then there is you![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev066801_MSG0004
rows.name:
My hope and desire is that these great warriors will
gather together in a gauntlet none will ever forget![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev066801_MSG0005
rows.name:
What say you? Do you see the same strength as I?
Do you know whom it is I speak of?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev066801_MSG0010
rows.name:
This should give us enough space to stage even the
roughest fight without causing trouble.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev066801_MSG0011
rows.name: ...Hmm? What am I doing, you ask?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev066801_MSG0012
rows.name:
Ha ha ha! Why, I merely seek a venue for the
Wrothian Battle Gauntlet—one of our finest traditions.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev066801_MSG0013
rows.name:
The "Outfitters," as you call them, use this area day
and night to test a whole slew of weapons.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev066801_MSG0014
rows.name:
It will not be easy, but provided I can convince them
to lend me the space, I can immediately set about
finding the city's strongest for the Gauntlet.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev066801_MSG0015
rows.name:
I trust you will compete as well, if you think you have
what it takes.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev066801_MSG0016
rows.name:
Preparations for the Wrothian Battle Gauntlet
are complete.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev066801_MSG0017
rows.name:
...Well, mostly complete. I still struggle to convince the
Outfitters to lend me their test hangar.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev066801_MSG0018
rows.name:
I originally tried asking some BLADEs face-to-face,
but they insisted I go through some sort of terminal
to make my request. What a bother![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev066801_MSG0020
rows.name:
Many powerful indigens still remain in the region.
Have you seen them?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev066801_MSG0021
rows.name:
Fallshorn Isle is home to a saltat an order of magnitude
stronger than any I reckon you have seen.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev066801_MSG0022
rows.name: And inside Talon Rock is a colony of vicious vespers![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev066801_MSG0023
rows.name:
I tell you, Mira is a fine planet to train on. Ha ha!
Truly it is![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev066801_MSG0024
rows.name:
I will take these great foes on, better myself as a
warrior, and return to challenge you again one day![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev066801_MSG0026
rows.name:
Ah! The strongest warrior in the land returns!
What a surprise to see you here.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev066801_MSG0027
rows.name: As you see, I am training. Would you care to spar?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev066801_MSG0028
rows.name:
...Ha! I jest. Mira has hordes of able opponents—
you need not waste your time with me.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev066801_MSG0029
rows.name:
We can save our rematch for the next Wrothian
Battle Gauntlet. I shall look forward to it![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev066801_MSG0030
rows.name:
Now then, back to training. With rivals like you near,
I cannot afford to laze about a second longer![ST:wait ]
